{"tid":1119071,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"舊時車票同紀念車票","createTime":"2019-04-21T16:39:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T04:59:00.000Z","uid":213401,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4e3c42318da0586e736c3f9481042b17cee741b8","tid":1119071,"uid":213401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T16:39:54.000Z","msg":"之前放錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講番主題先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好細過就好鍾意九鐵地鐵啲車飛，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以一直都有keep 起，<br />\n間唔中望下，<br />\n覺得以前啲車飛設計有心啲，<br />\n特別係九鐵果陣，真心覺得靚（左下角同右下角圖）<br />\n而家果啲係間唔時出紀念車飛覺得靚先買（左上角圖）<br />\n有時我都想買番舊時我冇草起嘅車票作紀念，<br />\n但已經唔知去邊買好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇巴絲都有keep 起呢啲車飛，可以影下相俾我都欣賞下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一部分嘅車飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t2r0Bex.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft2r0Bex.png&h=afd015d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6aaad3097a1cfacd8144da74a3a38036b1309b5","tid":1119071,"uid":248275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T18:31:50.000Z","msg":"嘩正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd566c5259aecf39ebefb846f2b7dc0d7146bf9","tid":1119071,"uid":193893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T18:37:48.000Z","msg":"嘩屌地鐵十周年都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f584e823b7eb4a0f3e30cb5668eeb95d98f18f91","tid":1119071,"uid":13151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T19:06:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eAOyhwo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeAOyhwo.png&h=d8e709d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一次搭地鐵嘅飛，好懷念細個個陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f8802d2b211f69ba46ec6b1d98ee3f0785aecd","tid":1119071,"uid":7355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T02:15:59.000Z","msg":"聯乘嗰啲正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc8d385599066798b60fde33015d8430ee1de863","tid":1119071,"uid":213401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cd566c5259aecf39ebefb846f2b7dc0d7146bf9","tid":1119071,"uid":193893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T18:37:48.000Z","msg":"嘩屌地鐵十周年都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T03:18:16.000Z","msg":"呢張係經典黎，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過係我老豆佢俾我，<br />\n果陣10週年未出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89aecb5829486091920aaad8b972c4089009f4c1","tid":1119071,"uid":213401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f584e823b7eb4a0f3e30cb5668eeb95d98f18f91","tid":1119071,"uid":13151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T19:06:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eAOyhwo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeAOyhwo.png&h=d8e709d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一次搭地鐵嘅飛，好懷念細個個陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T03:21:58.000Z","msg":"啲通用儲值票好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33214c3a14451a8b671826b7511d6971c363c381","tid":1119071,"uid":213401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0cd566c5259aecf39ebefb846f2b7dc0d7146bf9","tid":1119071,"uid":193893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T18:37:48.000Z","msg":"嘩屌地鐵十周年都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"